text: Jill Börresen (born 16 December 1973) is a South African archer. Börresen competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Jill Börresen ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:South African archers Category:Olympians for South Africa Category:Sportspeople from Durban
